<section class="block" aria-label="FAQ">
  <h2 style="font-size:20px; margin: 12px 0 8px;">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
  
  <div style="margin-bottom: 16px;">
    <h3 style="font-size:16px; margin: 8px 0 4px;">How do I save my progress?</h3>
    <p style="margin: 0 0 8px; color: var(--muted);">
      Your progress is automatically saved to your browser's local storage. You can continue where you left off.
    </p>

    <h3 style="font-size:16px; margin: 12px 0 4px;">Can I play offline?</h3>
    <p style="margin: 0 0 8px; color: var(--muted);">
      Yes! Once the game loads, you can play offline. Your scores will sync when you're back online.
    </p>

    <h3 style="font-size:16px; margin: 12px 0 4px;">How do I change the difficulty?</h3>
    <p style="margin: 0 0 8px; color: var(--muted);">
      Click the settings gear (âš™) in the game area to access difficulty options and other preferences.
    </p>

    <h3 style="font-size:16px; margin: 12px 0 4px;">Are there keyboard shortcuts?</h3>
    <p style="margin: 0 0 8px; color: var(--muted);">
      Yes! Press <strong>P</strong> to pause/resume, <strong>R</strong> to restart, <strong>Space</strong> to resume, and <strong>Escape</strong> for the menu.
    </p>

    <h3 style="font-size:16px; margin: 12px 0 4px;">How do I report a bug?</h3>
    <p style="margin: 0 0 8px; color: var(--muted);">
      Use the contact link in the footer or report issues directly through your browser's developer tools.
    </p>

    <h3 style="font-size:16px; margin: 12px 0 4px;">Can I customize the game appearance?</h3>
    <p style="margin: 0 0 8px; color: var(--muted);">
      Absolutely! Click the settings button to choose from 8 different background themes for the game area.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
